title: Arbor Snowboards :: Joe Bosler & The Northwest Powder
description:
Arbor Snowboards rider, Joe Bosler takes you on a tour of his average day in the Northwest slashing pillows and powder lines on his favorite snowboard, the Coda. It's just another day in the office for Boz.
